  "Description": [
    "Validator for reStructuredText documents with code blocks rstcheck validates the syntax of reStructuredText documents. Unlike other validators, it will also verify syntax correctness in nested code blocks for a variety of languages: . * Bash shell scripts * Doctest * C (C99) * C++ (C++11) * JSON * XML * Python * reStructuredText . rstcheck can also validate Sphinx documentation files if Sphinx is installed."
